description: Top floor two bedroom two bath loft like floor plan features  a generous size living room with wonderful light, roof top skyline views, hardwood floors, a ceiling height. Chef's kitchen with stainless appliances, gas cooking, custom built in dining table and breakfast island. Front facing primary with en suite bath, large second bedroom, second full bath, in unit laundry, AC, hardwood floors through out, elevator, professionally managed association, private storage closet, private roof deck space, two direct access under garage spaces included. Seller welcomes offers with requests for buyer concessions.
